credibility most commonly in relation to interest and inflation risks equities and currencies the firm rotates investments in asset allocation hedge design or the selection of alpha strategies aiming to add value and improve stability of return delivery details hidden slater investments ltd slater is a dedicated uk equity investor the large majority of the firms equity investments target midcap uk companies with marginal investments in smallcap and overseas stocks the funds may occasionally not be fully invested holding large amounts of cash or near cashto achieve capital growth the fund managers chase value stocks they target undervalued recovering companies following closely directors dealings and examining key quantitative data such as cash flow pricetosales ratio and pricetoresearch ratio they pick stocks without any particular reference to sector or index weightingsthe fund managers are personally invested in their fundsthe firm measure their funds performance against the fste all share details hidden herald investment management ltd himl is an active longterm manager which invests globally in listed and unlisted companies in the technology communications and media sectors they employ a bottomup approach to appraise potential investments fundamental financial analysis and traditional company research is supplemented both by company visits and regular meetings between himl and executive management teams details hidden herald investment management ltd himl is an active longterm manager which invests globally in listed and unlisted companies in the technology communications and media sectors they employ a bottomup approach to appraise potential investments fundamental financial analysis and traditional company research is supplemented both by company visits and regular meetings between himl and executive management teams details hidden river  mercantile asset management llp ramam is an active mediumterm manager which utilizes quantitative and fundamental analysis in their investment approach seeking absolute and relative returns they follow a specific inhouse process called pvt to select stocks seeking stocks with potential for creating shareholder value they asses the valuation gap between the stock market price and the midterm company value and aim to optimize entry and exit point timingthe firm combines quantitative and fundamental analysis believing that there are repeatable investment cycles that can be systematically exploited their global equity division employs a bottomup approach within a thematic backdrop aiming to select attractively priced stock from global companies which are benefitting from supportive trends the thematic backdrop helps to stimulate investment debate and highlights trends and areas of opportunityramam manages risk across multiple dimensions normal volatility market stress and permanent loss they seek to diversify across a range of asset classes or positions in order to reduce the risk of not meeting an investment objective and their teams typically design investment decisionmaking constraints in order to achieve and maintain diversification they seek to hedge risks where they expect client risk to be disproportionately high compared to the expected return andor its credibility most commonly in relation to interest and inflation risks equities and currencies the firm rotates investments in asset allocation hedge design or the selection of alpha strategies aiming to add value and improve stability of return delivery see  more listing with relsci professional start my free trial ➤ see  more recent transactions details hidden taptica international ltd purchases adinnovation inc from mitsubishi ufj capital co ltd smbc venture capital kk dbj capital co ltd  pending details hidden taptica ltd taptica international ltd purchase areaone ltd details hidden taptica international ltd purchases taptica ltd details hidden taptica international ltd issued ordinary shares transaction advisors companies ▾ broke